import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import './CoachesExec.css'; const CoachesExec = () => { const [teamMembers, setTeamMembers] = useState({ 'swim-coach': { name: 'Justin Konik', role: 'Swim Coach', image: '/images/swimcoach.png' }, 'co-president': { name: 'Jade Clement', role: 'Co-President', image: '/images/team-photo1.jpeg' }, 'co-president-2': { name: 'Marlene Garijo', role: 'Co-President', image: '/images/team-photo2.jpeg' }, 'treasurer': { name: 'Edward Ing', role: 'Treasurer', image: '/images/exec_treasurer.jpg' }, 'secretary': { name: 'Lauren Williams', role: 'Secretary', image: '/images/team-photo3.jpeg' }, 'social-coordinator': { name: 'Katy Tiper', role: 'Social Coordinator/Recruitment', image: '/images/team-photo4.jpg' }, 'social-media': { name: 'Paulette Dalton', role: 'Social Media Manager', image: '/images/exec_socialmedia.jpg' }, 'webmaster': { name: 'Ilan Gofman', role: 'Webmaster', image: '/images/icon.png' } }); // Load updated team member data from localStorage useEffect(() => { const loadTeamMembers = () => { const savedTeamMembers = localStorage.getItem('uoftTriTeamMembers'); if (savedTeamMembers) { try { const parsed = JSON.parse(savedTeamMembers); setTeamMembers(prev => ({ ...prev, ...parsed })); } catch (error) { console.error('Error parsing saved team members:', error); } } }; // Load on mount loadTeamMembers(); // Listen for storage changes (when returning from profile edit) const handleStorageChange = (e) => { if (e.key === 'uoftTriTeamMembers') { loadTeamMembers(); } }; window.addEventListener('storage', handleStorageChange); // Also check for changes when the page becomes visible again const handleVisibilityChange = () => { if (!document.hidden) { loadTeamMembers(); } }; document.addEventListener('visibilitychange', handleVisibilityChange); return () => { window.removeEventListener('storage', handleStorageChange); document.removeEventListener('visibilitychange', handleVisibilityChange); }; }, []); return (
